data.description: Welcome home! Have you always wanted a 2 story home in a high demand neighborhood on a cul-de-sac? We have the perfect home! 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths with nearly 3,000 sqft on the main & upper! Main level office, formal dining/living, massive dining area w/ fireplace. Spacious kitchen offers plentiful counter space, breakfast bar, abundant cabinetry & pantry. Huge family rm w/ fireplace & access to deck and large fenced yard. ML 1/2 bath and laundry too. Private master suite with W/I closet and bath. LL is partially finished w/ family rm, bar, 3rd fireplace, bathroom rough-in and tons of storage. Private master suite w/ WIC, sept tub/shower!
